---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';
---

<Base
  title="About"
  description="Fabien builds custom AI and automation systems for small teams in Dallas, TX."
>
  <section class="about-page">
    <div class="about-inner">
      <header class="about-header">
        <h1 data-en="About" data-es="Acerca">About</h1>
      </header>

      <div class="about-content">
        <div class="founder-section">
          <div class="founder-photo-placeholder" aria-label="Founder photo">
            <span class="photo-initials">F</span>
          </div>
          <div class="founder-text">
            <h2 class="founder-name">Fabien</h2>
            <p
              class="founder-role"
              data-en="Founder, JufipAI"
              data-es="Fundador, JufipAI"
            >
              Founder, JufipAI
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>

        <div class="about-body">
          <div class="about-section">
            <p>
              I started building automations because I got tired of watching
              smart people do dumb work. Copy this row. Paste it there. Send
              that email. Check the spreadsheet. Every single day.
            </p>
            <p>
              The first time I automated a 47-tab spreadsheet monster into a
              single dashboard, the office manager looked at me like I had
              performed a magic trick. It was just a Google Apps Script and
              some common sense. But it saved her 6 hours a week.
            </p>
            <p>
              That's what I do. I find the repetitive, soul-crushing processes
              that nobody talks about because "that's just how we do things"
              &mdash; and I make them disappear.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="about-section">
            <h2 data-en="What JufipAI does" data-es="Que hace JufipAI">
              What JufipAI does
            </h2>
            <p>
              We build custom automation systems. Not the drag-and-drop kind
              where you connect two apps and call it a day. Real systems that
              understand your business logic, handle edge cases, and actually
              work when you're not babysitting them.
            </p>
            <p>
              We use Claude for the parts that need thinking, Google Apps
              Script for the spreadsheet parts, and Cloud Functions when
              things need to talk to each other. No Zapier, no Make, no
              monthly subscription that costs more than the person it
              replaced.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="about-section">
            <h2 data-en="Who we work with" data-es="Con quien trabajamos">
              Who we work with
            </h2>
            <p>
              Most of our clients come from industries where there's a lot of
              paperwork and not enough time: staffing agencies drowning in
              applications, construction companies tracking injuries across 30
              sites, property managers juggling maintenance requests from 200
              units.
            </p>
            <p>
              We're based in Dallas but the automations work from anywhere. If
              your team is spending more time on data entry than actual work,
              we should talk.
            </p>
          </div>

          <div class="about-section">
            <h2
              data-en="Bilingual support"
              data-es="Soporte bilingue"
            >
              Bilingual support
            </h2>
            <p
              data-en="We serve English and Spanish-speaking teams. Because in Dallas, that's not optional &mdash; that's just Tuesday."
              data-es="Servimos equipos en ingles y espanol. Porque en Dallas, eso no es opcional &mdash; es simplemente un martes."
            >
              We serve English and Spanish-speaking teams. Because in Dallas,
              that's not optional &mdash; that's just Tuesday.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>
</Base>

<style>
  .about-page {
    padding: calc(var(--nav-height) + var(--space-xl)) 0 var(--space-xl);
  }

  .about-inner {
    max-width: var(--content-width);
    margin: 0 auto;
    padding: 0 var(--space-md);
  }

  .about-header {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .about-header h1 {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-display);
  }

  .founder-section {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-lg);
    margin-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    padding-bottom: var(--space-xl);
    border-bottom: 1px solid rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.06);
  }

  .founder-photo-placeholder {
    width: 120px;
    height: 120px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--bg-secondary);
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    justify-content: center;
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .photo-initials {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: 3rem;
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .founder-name {
    font-family: var(--font-display);
    font-size: var(--text-section);
    margin-bottom: 0.25rem;
  }

  .founder-role {
    font-family: var(--font-mono);
    font-size: var(--text-small);
    color: var(--text-muted);
  }

  .about-body {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-xl);
  }

  .about-section h2 {
    font-family: var(--font-body);
    font-weight: 600;
    font-size: 1.25rem;
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    color: var(--text-primary);
  }

  .about-section p {
    margin-bottom: var(--space-md);
    line-height: 1.8;
  }

  .about-section p:last-child {
    margin-bottom: 0;
  }

  @media (max-width: 640px) {
    .founder-section {
      flex-direction: column;
      text-align: center;
    }
  }
</style>
